IMAPStore personal-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User yasser.kaddoura19@gmail.com
AuthMechs XOAUTH2
PassCMD "mailctl access yasser.kaddoura19@gmail.com"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore personal-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/gmail/INBOX
Flatten .

Channel gmail
Expunge Both
Far :personal-remote:
Near :personal-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 0
ExpireUnread no

